Introduction

Park Minju is a South Korean singer under Belift Lab. She is best known as the main vocalist of the girl group ILLIT.

In June 2023, she participated in HYBE and Belift Lab's survival show called R U Next?, where she was chosen by the label to be the third member to debut in the final group ILLIT.
